reviewtext: I tried to use it in my 2008 Ford Explorer factory CD changer.  No luck.  It would just spit it out when it got to the brush section.I know some others had said it worked for them in their car decks and changers, but sadly, it did not work for me.If anyone has any ideas or tips that might help it work, I'm all ears.
summary: Didn't work for me, but would probably work elsewhere.
